title: Natures_Way_Guide_to_Breastfeeding
description: Developed by international board-certified lactation consultant Hayley Wagner, this guide to breast-feeding will give you the skills and confidence you need to get it right from the very start. The video features multiple-angle close-ups and slow-motion clips of latching and side-by-side comparisons of good vs. poor positioning. The course covers most classroom topics, including how long to breast-feed, pumping and storage, mom&#039;s diet and more.
